OL,3,CWhat's on the menu at the White House
OL,4,Cstate dinner?
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump and the First
OL,7,FLady welcomed King Charles III and
OL,8,FQueen Camilla to the White House state
OL,9,Fdinner on the second day of their
OL,10,Fstate visit of the US.
OL,12,FHigh-profile guests enjoyed a four-
OL,13,Fcourse menu, alongside musical
OL,14,Fentertainment, and speeches from both
OL,15,Fthe King and Trump.
OL,17,FThe aim of the dinner is to "honor the
OL,18,FSpecial Relationship between the
OL,19,FUnited States and the United Kingdom."
OL,21,FBut what was on the menu?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
