OL,3,CWhat's on the menu at the White House
OL,4,Cstate dinner?
OL,6,FFirst CourseJThe first course offers
OL,7,Fgarden herb veloute, with a
OL,8,F"refreshing" hearts of palm salad,
OL,9,Ftoasted shallots and a "whisper" of
OL,10,Fmicro mint.
OL,12,FSecond CourseJThe second course is a
OL,13,Fspring herb ravioli, featuring herbs
OL,14,Ffrom the White House Kitchen Garden,
OL,15,Ffilled with creamy ricotta, morels,
OL,16,Fwith a light parmesan emulsion.
OL,18,FThird Course
OL,26,@oD@Srr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
