OL,3,CWhat's on the menu at the White House
OL,4,Cstate dinner?
OL,6,FThe third course is made of a classic
OL,7,Fdover sole meuniere, in a nutty brown
OL,8,Fbutter. The fish is accompanied by
OL,9,Ftender spring ramps, sweet snow peas,
OL,10,Flayered potatoes pave, and a vibrant
OL,11,Fparsley oil for a refined, seasonal
OL,12,Ffinish.
OL,14,FDessert
OL,16,FFor dessert, guests will be served a
OL,17,Fsweet beehive shaped chocolate gateau
OL,18,Fwith a vanilla bean cremeux custard,
OL,19,Fset inside with an almond joconde. The
OL,20,Fbeehive will come with creme fraiche
OL,21,Fice cream and White House honey.
