OL,3,CWhat's on the menu at the White House
OL,4,Cstate dinner?
OL,6,FDinner was served with a selection of
OL,7,Fwines to "complement the menu" and
OL,8,F"celebrate the strength of American
OL,9,Fwinemaking":
OL,11,FThe guests of honour, the King and
OL,12,FQueen, were joined by a number of high-
OL,13,Fprofile guests during the evening.
OL,15,FThese included Amazon founder Jeff
OL,16,FBezos and Apple CEO Tim Cook.
OL,18,FJD Vance, Marco Rubio and Pete Hegseth
OL,19,Fjoined other members of Trump's
OL,20,Fcabinet at the dinner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
