OL,3,CWhat's on the menu at the White House
OL,4,Cstate dinner?
OL,6,FThe President's family were also
OL,7,Finvited: Eric Trump and his wife Lara,
OL,8,Fand Ivanka Trump alongside her
OL,9,Fhusband, and Special Peace Envoy,
OL,10,FJared Kushner.
OL,12,FGolfer Rory McIlroy also made the
OL,13,Flist. The Master's champion getting a
OL,14,Fshout-out from the President for his
OL,15,F"unconquerable courage".
OL,17,FA Royal toast
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
