OL,3,CWhat's on the menu at the White House
OL,4,Cstate dinner?
OL,6,FThe King opened his toast with
OL,7,Fgratitude for the President's
OL,8,F"generous hospitality" and his
OL,9,F"courage", following shots being fired
OL,10,Fat Saturday's White House
OL,11,FCorrespondents dinner.
OL,13,FHe went on to comment on Trump's
OL,14,Frecent comments, that without the US
OL,15,F"European countries would be speaking
OL,16,FGerman", joking that "if it wasn't for
OL,17,Fus, you'd be speaking French!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
