OL,3,CWhat's on the menu at the White House
OL,4,Cstate dinner?
OL,6,FHe added, "of course, we both love our
OL,7,FFrench cousins greatly, and we three
OL,8,Fstates are not only bound by our
OL,9,Fshared values, but by a profound
OL,10,Fbelief that, together, we are more
OL,11,Fthan the sum of our parts."
OL,13,FCharles III also looked ahead to the
OL,14,Fupcoming World Cup, reminding the
OL,15,FPresident that as well as the US,
OL,16,FCanada will be hosting the tournament,
OL,17,F"so in one sense, Mr President, as
OL,18,FHeads of State, we are joint hosts!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
